Package UserSystem

Class User

Object
User
public class User extends Object
The User class represents a user in the system. It can be used to represent both patients and staff members, providing various attributes such as name, ID, gender, role, and contact information.

      public User(String id, String name, LocalDate dateOfBirth, Gender gender, String phoneNumber, String email, String bloodType, Role role)
      Constructs a User object representing a patient with default password.
      Parameters:
      id - the ID of the patient.
      name - the name of the patient.
      dateOfBirth - the date of birth of the patient.
      gender - the gender of the patient.
      phoneNumber - the phone number of the patient.
      email - the email of the patient.
      bloodType - the blood type of the patient.
      role - the role of the patient (e.g., PATIENT).
